{"tid":2515224,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[畫鞋] 畫咗個深海寶箱上對鞋度","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T03:24:51.000Z","uid":202514,"like":101,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"49dbacec42185bc567ba4fb19ac61dbb07c80367","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:16:46.000Z","msg":"Hi，又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次post返舊作<br />\n就係每次有人問襟唔襟用我都攞出來講嘅嗰對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfRRhFhnR6GemmEYJkgkfTKGiYQncZ6vQuhKhat2htGgQ?filename=Np54dZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNp54dZW.jpg&h=11c2869a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQBwbjoSUj1dLzRxk7VtvXimj2ZoxPQcxWJDUTPJszbEd?filename=cVoYirD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVoYirD.jpg&h=0b28eea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本個樣係咁<br />\n純灰白銀三色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcbJHXgwzKGutY4t9rCQRv7odhDp7Ryz2fkrA3XKW9JdH?filename=3AoENjZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AoENjZ.jpg&h=9213086a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始淨係想畫木紋，但唔知畫咩主題好<br />\n因為呢對鞋會自動綁鞋帶<br />\n綁嗰陣個feel好似八爪魚腳勒緊咁<br />\n聯想埋一齊之後就諗到畫深海寶箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加左啲細節比如藤壺、生銹嘅寶箱嗰條鐵邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXRnZDzSMDaMMm345PvyYprRoz339WQ22bWkgVaC7aoWW?filename=2W4gPzA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2W4gPzA.jpg&h=3c918658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNU8Ng1w3siRAf3jyeqDaLj3qmzB2797jjdjk38sj4wSL?filename=r2K1geC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2K1geC.jpg&h=1352029a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbiEZQbKX7nTKDcNq2kyXgZXjmS6nMVc2fzVhmTc9Dkz6?filename=7fGfkGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fGfkGi.jpg&h=957977f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbAms3gM3dgRV8s7fAmHzPQyRDU8f99sobEpVaXSevuS4?filename=3LhNWeD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LhNWeD.jpg&h=efb54035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYb4GHPjEogZi2vLm2A7XnmadufAJN7acpAbcW5n99qFo?filename=jg5cnUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjg5cnUD.jpg&h=675470ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWf6z5KFXnLckSCxirqh6BHV5Qc1LZ9eRVhS4qSaPPuqH?filename=05HaT1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05HaT1k.jpg&h=473f68e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得唔錯嘅話，可以支持下小弟<br />\nFollow返個ig : yauyau_jy<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/yauyau_jy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyauyau_jy&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=6048d631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/yauyau_jy</a><br />\n<br />\n不定期會有改鞋嘅post/story"},{"pid":"8bffad7ba9ec451f787f9337accf565a83ce8cbb","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6b2a901b2fa3ae0aca4eef98111a733d988b24","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f788ce0343756ee2a13329128d7c0be0403161","tid":2515224,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7589505d9fbfded3a8ccc1c298a0dba2598e6726","tid":2515224,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bbb89dc73a6d6cc80b7602e16a607689b74a27","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5d0af52f6c03a5618a64074082a599460f4cca","tid":2515224,"uid":316171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb84cfaeedc13d05e41e8972abbbe59ffa1617c1","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:28:24.000Z","msg":"補少少過程圖<br />\n以前成日整一個step就影一張<br />\n近排次次整好一邊腳先記得影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始噴左個鞋面先<br />\n用咗幾種藍色同湖水綠做渾濁嗰種feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZhvs6xt31KKXRZLSDsum7xW88K9Fws3SnVx3htJ3L9Vv?filename=3AfWPCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AfWPCf.png&h=41ea847e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmddFZTzSttZJxqYVd4KhCcv5TsSW3MWGvNbRmAcs4GTZQ?filename=Q01i2Xk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ01i2Xk.png&h=1946a452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就遮個swoosh仔油木紋<br />\n底啡+幾種深啡慢慢手畫<br />\n個swoosh仔之後上返金色<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbUrUiSpN9438MbbjcqnftZGpzTL5qZNoNTxrNhzTA2fe?filename=enQS7o6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenQS7o6.png&h=d89dabe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主體得純顏色同Pattern嗰陣<br />\n有少少寡<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUeQYmBdYz8wqwyq7WumQRyNLcV41XH9bSsBcyYv2Dcjh?filename=w3Ohy4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3Ohy4a.png&h=d012e4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就慢慢用畫筆加返啲八爪魚腳同藤壺<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf3t1WzKCk3qDkGDEXRG6XiojVugg8GpYgivGwSVsHk7N?filename=VU0cnXz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVU0cnXz.png&h=05642447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bc9fba222e1f1d6c2c885ea08ab0017c316b5e9","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a133e92c85f0d1e791aafd329834ac42f553e6c","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4501200110739946402d2f3f73ea895c50003f1b","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"l