score":0,"quote":{"pid":"726d93652008c7fecd5be0714a60204600064e82","tid":2515224,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"瞓醒就有靚鞋睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"多謝讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6865ec828db9a44764c321f95f768c9824d0cbee","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e504ba9a605bbd9a14f307be97073ea05a52278e","tid":2515224,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"將個大剔畫成陰莖有冇得諗？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"有，但我唔會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574affd9581df6a665fe78092c1f9afd5397afd0","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ad30f279b58bbcb1704dd6bcc0fc233fc14567","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20cc4049b46bb5f73b2bedbd8a757ae73c3f216","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"cb84cfaeedc13d05e41e8972abbbe59ffa1617c1","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:28:24.000Z","msg":"補少少過程圖<br />\n以前成日整一個step就影一張<br />\n近排次次整好一邊腳先記得影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始噴左個鞋面先<br />\n用咗幾種藍色同湖水綠做渾濁嗰種feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3AfWPCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AfWPCf.png&h=41ea847e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q01i2Xk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ01i2Xk.png&h=1946a452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就遮個swoosh仔油木紋<br />\n底啡+幾種深啡慢慢手畫<br />\n個swoosh仔之後上返金色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enQS7o6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenQS7o6.png&h=d89dabe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主體得純顏色同Pattern嗰陣<br />\n有少少寡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3Ohy4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3Ohy4a.png&h=d012e4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就慢慢用畫筆加返啲八爪魚腳同藤壺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VU0cnXz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVU0cnXz.png&h=05642447&s={SIZE}\" />"}}